7️⃣ Access Profile:-
Kya hai?
Access Profile = Application access ka bundle / package.
Isme entitlements (permissions) group kiye jate hain taaki ek hi request me access mil jaye.
Short Answer:-
👉 Access Profile में user application के entitlements (permissions / groups / roles) के लिए request करता है।
Access Profile kyu bhejte (request) hai?
Access Profile isliye bhejte hain taaki user ko kisi application ka access mil sake.

()Access Profile Important Attributes:-
Attribute	Kya karta hai
name------------Access profile ka naam
source----------Application source
entitlements----Permissions list
requestable-----User request kar sakta hai ya nahi
description-----Access ka purpose

()Access Profile में क्या-क्या होता है:-
Access Profile के अंदर:-
Entitlements
Approval workflow
Owner
Description
Source (Application)

()Example:-
Access Profile:-
HR App Access

Inside Access Profile:-
Entitlement 1 → HR_Read
Entitlement 2 → HR_Report

अगर user HR App Access request करेगा तो दोनों entitlements मिल सकते हैं।

()IdentityNow Access Request Flow:-
User
↓
Access Request
↓
Access Profile choose
↓
Manager / Owner approval
↓
Provisioning
↓
Application में access create
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
()system/admin side se Access Profile create aur manage kar raha hai.
Ye sab SailPoint IdentityNow ke REST APIs ko call karke hota hai.
hummne abhi tak koi access request nahi kiya access profile ko choose karne ke liye:-
-----------------------------------------:-----------------------------------

1️⃣ Java Code – Access Profile Create (API Call)
import java.net.HttpURLConnection;
import java.net.URL;
import java.io.OutputStream;
import java.io.InputStreamReader;
import java.io.BufferedReader;

public class CreateAccessProfile {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        try {

            URL url = new URL("https://tenant.api.identitynow.com/v3/access-profiles");

            HttpURLConnection conn = (HttpURLConnection) url.openConnection();

            conn.setRequestMethod("POST");
            conn.setRequestProperty("Authorization", "Bearer ACCESS_TOKEN");
            conn.setRequestProperty("Content-Type", "application/json");
            conn.setDoOutput(true);

            String jsonInput = "{"
                    + "\"name\":\"SAP Finance Access\","
                    + "\"description\":\"Finance team SAP access profile\","
                    + "\"requestable\":true"
                    + "}";

            OutputStream os = conn.getOutputStream();
            os.write(jsonInput.getBytes());
            os.flush();

            BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(
                    new InputStreamReader(conn.getInputStream()));

            String line;
            while ((line = br.readLine()) != null) {
                System.out.println(line);
            }

            conn.disconnect();

        } catch (Exception e) {
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
2️⃣ JSON Request Body
{
  "name": "SAP Finance Access",
  "description": "Finance team SAP access profile",
  "requestable": true
}
3️⃣ Output (API Response)
{
  "id": "2c9180857a6f9999997a6f999999abcd",
  "name": "SAP Finance Access",
  "description": "Finance team SAP access profile",
  "requestable": true,
  "enabled": true
}

Matlab:-
Access Profile Successfully Created
