1️⃣ requestedFor ID kya hai?
"requestedFor": "2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c1111111111"
Ye Identity (User) ID hoti hai.
Matlab:-
User → Rahul
User ID → 2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c1111111111

System ko pata chale:-
kis user ke liye access request ho rahi hai

2️⃣ accessProfileIds kya hai?
"accessProfileIds": [
"2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c2222222222"
]
Ye Access Profile ID hoti hai.

Example:-
Access Profile → Salesforce Read Access
Access Profile ID → 2c9180847e9b1a1f017e9c2222222222

Matlab:-
user kis access profile ka access maang raha hai
