()system/admin side se Access Profile create aur manage kar raha hai.
Ye sab SailPoint IdentityNow ke REST APIs ko call karke hota hai.
hummne abhi tak koi access request nahi kiya access profile ko choose karne ke liye,
lekin abb hum access profile ko choose karenge access request karne ke liye:-

3️⃣ Access Request JSON ka matlab:-
{
 "requestedFor": "UserID",
 "accessProfileIds": ["AccessProfileID"]
}
Meaning:-
UserID → kis user ko access chahiye
AccessProfileID → kaunsa access chahiye.

()Access Request kya hai?
--Access Request = user kisi application ka access maangta hai.
Access Profile ek permission bundle hota hai, 
jabki Access Request wo process hai jisme user us Access Profile ka access maangta hai.

Access Request ka use:-
1️⃣ Application access lene ke liye
User kisi bhi app ka access request karta hai.
Example;-
Salesforce
ServiceNow
Jira
SAP

2️⃣ Role access lene ke liye:-
Example:-
HR Role
Finance Role
Developer Role

3️⃣ Temporary access lene ke liye;
Example:-
Developer ko 2 din ke liye production access chahiye.
